nodes.text: CF-3871 was a First Order stormtrooper who served under Lieutenant Wulfgar Kath. When Kath was deployed to Batuu to find the Resistance spy Vi Moradi, CF-3871 was one of the troopers who accompanied him. CF-3871 and CF-3363 confronted the smuggler Zade Kalliday in an alley, but were shot dead by Moradi.
